interpretation:
The "Selfie" card represents self-exploration and self-expression. It encourages you to take a closer look at yourself and the image you project to others. It reminds you that you have the power to create your own narrative and control how you are perceived by the world. This card also highlights the importance of self-care and self-love. 

If you draw this card, it may be a sign to take a step back and evaluate your relationship with yourself. Are you being true to who you are? Are you taking care of your mental and physical health? This card is a reminder to prioritize yourself and your needs.
